XX22 CK_PHI1_BAR CK_PHI1 N001 Vdd N001 tgate params: L=0.28u Wn={Wn_d} Wp={Wp_d} M=1
R1 N016 N015 1000G
R2 N012 Vctr 1000G
R3 Vop N005 1000G
R4 N006 Vop 1000G
R5 Vbias NC_01 1000G
R6 NC_02 Vbias 1000G
R7 NC_03 Vocm_ref 1000G
R8 Vocm_ref NC_04 1000G
XX6 CK_PHI1 CK_PHI1_BAR N010 Vdd Vom tgate params: L=0.28u Wn=1u Wp=3u M=1
